imating the number of solutions of systems of diophantine equations over\nintegers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Apr 2013 23:06:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Dec 2015 14:33:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-12-02"}
