alactic center and is\nslowly-accelerated without any drastic energy injection like starburst events.\nThese transonic outflows may contribute secularly to the metal enrichment of\nthe intergalactic medium.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Apr 2013 08:17:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
