s stable equilibrium when reach at a critical height. With some\nreasonable parameters, and inherent physical conditions the model describes the\nnon-radial ascending motion of the flux rope in the corona, its stopping at\nsome height, and thereafter the downward motion, which are in good agreement\nwith the observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Apr 2013 09:52:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-15"}
